            "class": "ital",
            "text": "wizards.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " The source of all these modes of soothsaying was Babylon. Like the first king of Israel, Manasseh appears to have despaired of help or counsel from Jehovah. (Comp. ",
